Quote:  His latest concept for looking at how the city might develop in the future is the "big hairy-arsed project." Speaking at the council's strategic and annual planning working group meeting yesterday, he came up with the BHAP as an alternative to the council's traditional way of eking outs its budget by nibbling away at all the worthy but large projects people are clamouring for.
